When you run:
sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/your_domain
Make sure to use a sample like the one below:

server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;

    server_name alexmichealserver.ddns.net;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://44.203.88.229:8081;
        include proxy_params;
    }
}
